2025 Wren emote
2025 Adetunde emotes
“2025” Title
Firework Rocket Launcher Lobby Gadget

data.name: You Met Interstellar Messenger, KatieCreative! 🌙
data.description:
Hi, little Souls! I'm KatieCreative and my pronouns are she / her 

It's nice to meet you, I see you found me while I was wandering around the spaceship trying to explore this wonderful world, 

I'm your one and only angel sent from above! Haven't you heard of me? I hope you do know now. 
I can't wait to meet you in this wonderful place! It's so magical and pretty just like me! 

What do I do you may be wondering... Well....

•  I'm a self taught artist and editor! (Which means I learn everything by myself) 

•  I specialize in creating characters and giving them life, it's what I'm known for on my platform, 

All my platforms are @ CAmintronics101 except for Roblox that's KatieCreative102

data.name: The Thievery of Crystals
data.description:
Moonlight here; reporting live from an aquatic realm known as the epitome of shame, and sadness. The dark shallow waters, encompass the decaying coral reefs, and abandoned village homes. Distant wails of deep sea creatures can be heard miles away... Will we be able to free them from the curses of Archon, and restore what was rightfully lost? Or will we succumb to the darkness...

Description by Umoyae

data.description:

data.name: Premium Payout Or "Difficult" Badge, Call It
data.description:
In Endless, reach room number 500.

theres no reaching room 1000th room badge cuz like do u actually want to do that? like sure its a nice round number but cmon now WHY would you put yourself through that. theres no point, theres no goal. youd be wasting your time, and for what? some achivement that in the grand scheme of things, no-one will care about? like wow congrats you held W for a few hours and pressed E every now and then. like this badge is just here for completionists, and because some people would obviously be complaining like "oooh why doesnt endless have a hard-to-get badge :(((" even tho its not really that difficult, more-so an endurance test. an endurance test against boredom.

if you go for the badge, kudos I guess. thanks for the playtime &/or premium payout.

Drawn by @TheForgottenArrow

data.name: THE ACCIDENT
data.description:
Uncover the past. 

No weapons have ever been proven to work against the eldritch terror. Before the accident, bob was temporarily inactive. The only species left by the terror, roaming in anarchy, yet all united under the goal of finding a way to stop the beast before it's too late. The strongest group, calling themselves the "opposition", owned a small research facility, hidden deep underground. They would research, and do countless experiments to learn more about how bob works, his traits and most importantly; how to combat him. The opposition would conduct experiments to attempt replication of a docile version of bob. A version that they could control. Hundreds of experiments, yet none seem to be able to replicate the power of him. Hope is not lost, as a member returns to the facility with a sample of dark blob matter which they presume some lost tissue belonging to bob. They extract the DNA and experiment with it. Progress is being made, until one day, all is lost.

R O B
8 0 8

data.description: Ice7 is a totes awesome scripter dude! He made the whole inventory system! He is also working on mobile phones to text your friends on and access numerous features. Remember when you would sink to the bottom of the pool like a rock, if you had a giant skirt on or mermaid tail? No longer! data.name: Dewdrop Showers 2022
data.description:
You Experienced The First-Ever Dewdrop Showers In RH (2022)! 💧

The first signs of Spring naturally stir excitement into the fae, but such overflowing exuberance caused these magical meteorological marvels! It is only through the reflection of downpouring droplets do we see the robustly resilient rainbow, & we are enlightened in the realization that even cloudburst calamities ought to be celebrated... Did you at least bring a sturdy umbrella?! (description by stixxntricks, badge art by ixchoco_)

data.name: Royale Spring 2022!
data.description:
You Experienced An Eggcellent Egg Hunt In Royale High (2022)! 🥚 

Once the clouds part, all eyes turn to the skies yet again when a midnight thicket situates itself above Divinia Park! While scouring for eggs, as the ebbing moon reflects on the glistening waters of a glowing grove, spare a second to reflect upon the state of our existence this spring. For as the elevated moon affects even that which is far beneath it, so does your minuet ripple in the ponds of life. Leave no trails of chocolate wrappers & be mindful of your footing, for this soil never forgets all those who sully it...
(written by stixxntricks, badge art by ixchoco)

Leave no trails of chocolate wrappers & be mindful of your footing, for this soil never forgets all those who sully it...
(written by stixxntricks, badge art by ixchoco)

data.name: Cradled In Frost
data.description:
Royalty cascades above, but now finds itself affixed in ice...

What once ruled the stars above now finds itself still & sleepily encased in the star-twìnkling snow...

When comets cascade & befriend a starry regal crown...

Stars frozen on my form, I reach up to them again once upon every icy storm.

Above the stars, fell a frozen whim. Encased in ice, they rule from within.

data.name: Journey Into Dreams...
data.description:

data.name: Skies Above
data.description:
In the chill of morning, the veil between world's thins..

In icy realms where whispers flow,
a Glacial Angel, soft and slow,
Spreads silver light from wing to wing,
and crowns the earth in frost’s first ring.

Through dawn’s cool veil, her fingers trace
a lace of ice on nature’s face.
Beneath her watch, the morning breathes,
in frozen calm, through glistening leaves.

data.name: Soldats de ma Vieille Garde
data.description:
(Badge may require to rejoin, or to press P multiple times)
In order to get this badge, you must complete the following tasks:

1. Get a KDR of 10 or above.
2. Save 51 teammates from being grabbed by a zombie.
3. Stay alive for 35 rounds, without restarting, on Endless. It can start at any wave, just as long as you stay alive for 35 rounds in total.
4. Win 30 times or above in the campaign mode.
5. Acquire the following badges: Old Yeller, Cold Front, Explosive Retreat, and Deliverance from the Catacombs.

This unlocks the Old Guard Regiment under France.

Given to those whom sacrificed themselves for the betterment of their fellow soldier.
Obtaining this badge unlocks Chaplain and the Cross Necklace.

To unlock this achievement, you must:
- Save 150 teammates from being grabbed.
- Kill 75 runners pinning your teammate.
- Obtain the badge "Vos Enterrement".
- Heal teammates over 50 times (as Surgeon).

data.name: Bricksmith
data.description: The Bricksmith badge is earned by having a popular personal place. Once your place has been visited 1000 times, you will receive this award. Robloxians with Bricksmith badges are accomplished builders who were able to create a place that people wanted to explore a thousand times. They no doubt know a thing or two about putting bricks together.
data.displayDescription: The Bricksmith badge is earned by having a popular personal place. Once your place has been visited 1000 times, you will receive this award. Robloxians with Bricksmith badges are accomplished builders who were able to create a place that people wanted to explore a thousand times. They no doubt know a thing or two about putting bricks together.

data.name: Homestead
data.description: The homestead badge is earned by having your personal place visited 100 times. Players who achieve this have demonstrated their ability to build cool things that other Robloxians were interested enough in to check out. Get a jump-start on earning this reward by inviting people to come visit your place.

data.name: Veteran
data.description: This decoration is awarded to all citizens who have played RetroStudio for at least a year. It recognizes stalwart community members who have stuck with us over countless releases and have helped shape RetroStudio into the game that it is today. These medalists are the true steel, the core of the RetroStudio history ... and its future.
